data.description: Property can finally be shown! Like living on the Wilshire Corridor! This beautiful & unique penthouse with 24 hour guard gated concierge service is located in one of the Valley's most prestigious condominium developments, Encino Park West! Elegant and dramatic 2 story lobby with floor to ceiling mirrors and crystal chandeliers. This penthouse features 2 bedrooms and 2 baths. Picturesque views of treetops, mountains, foliage and a park are seen from this light and bright condominium featuring towering ceilings and walls of windows. Formal entry area with custom light fixture. Expansive porcelain tile flooring. Living room with conversation area. Dramatic archway, granite counters, newer stove, stainless steel faucet and huge pantry adorn this redecorated "Tuscany" style kitchen. Huge master suite with "wood style" tile floor, fan lamp, walk in closet plus additional wardrobe closet. Spacious master bath with separate shower stall and tub. Closets galore . Amenities in this absolutely meticulously maintained building which has recently been painted and has a new roof (installation in progress) features a pool, spa, party room, sauna and gym. This penthouse is perfectly located to all of Encino's finest shops and restaurants. Bring your upscale buyers!
